&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience as a Sales Engineer, with a proven track record of working with Fortune 500 companies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Information Technology, Information and Computer Technology, Networking, IT Security from an accredited university.&lt;/li&gt;
